Photo, A life in the balance -- The scene as police tried to persuade Victor 
Bruno, 24, a deaf mute, to leave a platform extending from the roof of a New 
York highrise. With the help of two sisters who knew sign language, police were 
able to lure Bruno close enough so that they could grab him and pull him to 
safety. Associated Press 
</P>
