<P>
NBC News substitute anchor Mary Alice Williams is expecting her first baby 
early next year, the network announced Wednesday. Williams, who joined NBC last 
spring after eight years at Cable News Network, is married to Mark Haefeli, a 
CNN correspondent in New York. ALEENE MacMINN 
