<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY WORKERS OCCUPYING 5 TRAILERS PURCHASED AS HOUSING FOR HOMELESS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DEAN MURPHY, Times Staff Writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
