in Orange. Neither he nor his brother was home when $300,000 blaze started, and 
his parents were in Georgia. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Martha 
Sanchez, 32, watches fire at her apartment complex. ; Map, Orange County Fires, 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
