which is operating in "basically a testing period," a park official said. 
AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Some guests waited in long 
lines to test the speedy water ride, which was closed for half an hour 
Wednesday afternoon to iron out a glitch. 
</P>
