<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN GABRIEL VALLEY DIGEST: MONTEREY PARK; 
</P>
<P>
AIR CLEANUP TO BE DISCUSSED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Officials of the U. S. Environmental Protection Agency will discuss cleanup 
activities at the Operating Industries Inc. landfill in Monterey Park at a 
community meeting from 7 p.m. to 9:30 p.m. Wednesday at the Montebello High 
School cafeteria, 2100 Cleveland Ave., Montebello. 
</P>
<P>
The EPA will present the latest results of its program to monitor air near the 
dump for toxic emissions. Representatives of companies that shipped hazardous 
waste to the dump and are undertaking cleanup work under EPA supervision will 
answer questions about the project. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Brief; Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
