Bench, now a Reds television broadcaster, said he ate the cereal as a child and 
recalls seeing a picture of Olympic pole-vaulter Bob Richards on the box. 
</P>
<P>
The Minnesota Twins were honored with having their team picture on Wheaties 
boxes after the Twins won the 1987 World Series. 
